trans-unit.source: Specifies the painting style applied to one <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"></xref> contained in a form.
trans-unit.target: いずれかに適用される描画スタイルを指定<xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip"></xref>フォームに含まれています。

trans-unit.source: You cannot explicitly set the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> to Custom.
trans-unit.target: 明示的に設定することはできません、<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>カスタム</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>。

trans-unit.source: However, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> returns Custom when the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.Renderer%2A?displayProperty=fullName> is set to an extension of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderer> class that is not <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer>.
trans-unit.target: ただし、<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>カスタムを返すとき<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.Renderer%2A?displayProperty=fullName><xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderer><xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer>または<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer></xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer>ないであるクラス</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderer>の拡張に設定されている</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.Renderer%2A?displayProperty=fullName></xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.RenderMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Indicates that the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip.RenderMode*> is not determined by the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripManager"></xref> or the use of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripRenderer"></xref> other than <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProfessionalRenderer"></xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripSystemRenderer"></xref>
